casebody.data:
John C. CARNEY, Governor of Delaware, Petitioner
v.
James R. ADAMS No. 19-309 Supreme Court of the United States. December 6, 2019

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit granted. In addition to the questions presented by the petition, the parties is directed to brief and argue the following question: Whether respondent has demonstrated Article III standing.
